  "text": "The genome sequences were searched by annotation as well as by homology against the protein sequence of the closest known AHAS gene (T. maritima). b Alphanumeric codes indicate the locus tag of the gene in the corresponding genome; -, not present. c The presence of a complete set of ilv genes was checked. d This strain was recently suggested to be named \"Mesotoga prima\" and to be the first member of a new sub-group of mesophilic Thermotogales [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
